
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Tourist Places in India</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CDN for Carousel -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container mt-4">
        <h1 class="text-center">Tourist Places in India</h1>
        <div id="touristCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
            <div class="carousel-inner">
                <div class="carousel-item active">
                    <img src="/images/tajmahal.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Taj Mahal">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h5>Taj Mahal</h5>
                        <p>The Taj Mahal is a white marble mausoleum located in Agra.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="/images/jaipur.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Jaipur">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h5>Jaipur</h5>
                        <p>Known as the "Pink City", Jaipur is famous for its forts and palaces.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="/images/goa.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Goa">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h5>Goa</h5>
                        <p>Famous for its beautiful beaches and vibrant nightlife.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="/images/kerala.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Kerala">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h5>Kerala</h5>
                        <p>Known for its backwaters and houseboats, Kerala is a paradise for nature lovers.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#touristCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
            </button>
            <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#touristCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bootstrap JS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
